-- Austrian president signs Hypo "haircut" law
-- By Georgina Prodhan
-- Thu Jul 31, 2014 05:05AM EDT
-- None



VIENNA, July 31 (Reuters) - Austrian President Heinz Fischer has signed a law that will wipe out the claims of subordinated debt holders in nationalised bank Hypo Alpe Adria [HAABI.UL], his office said on Thursday.

